casebody.data:
No. 128,

Orig.

Alaska v. United States. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 532 U. S. 1017.]

Motion of the Special Master for fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $20,136.90 for the period April 17 through October 16, 2001, to be paid equally by the parties.
